# Autopus Branding Formats

> Format specifications for Autopus visual feedback and progress displays.
> These formats MUST be used by all agents as defined per subcommand context.

> **Canonical Source**: This file is the single source of truth for all Autopus visual output formats.
> All agents and rules MUST reference this file rather than duplicating format definitions inline.

---

## A0: Session Start Format

Display on the first response of a new conversation (Tier 1 — Session Start).

**Case 1: SPECs exist**

```
🐙 Autopus ─────────────────────────
  프로젝트: {project-name} | 모드: {mode}
  SPEC: {draft}개 draft · {approved}개 approved · {implemented}개 구현중 · {completed}개 완료
  최근 완료: {SPEC-ID} ({title})
  다음: {next-step recommendation}
```

**Case 2: No SPECs**

```
🐙 Autopus ─────────────────────────
  프로젝트: {project-name} | 모드: {mode}
  SPEC: 없음
  다음: /auto plan "기능 설명" 으로 시작하세요
```

**Field mappings:**
- `{project-name}` — project name from autopus.yaml
- `{mode}` — current mode (full, lite, etc.) from autopus.yaml
- `{draft}` — count of SPECs in draft status
- `{approved}` — count of SPECs in approved status
- `{implemented}` — count of SPECs currently being implemented
- `{completed}` — count of SPECs fully completed
- `{SPEC-ID}` — identifier of most recently completed SPEC (e.g., `SPEC-UX-001`)
- `{title}` — title of most recently completed SPEC
- `{next-step recommendation}` — contextual suggestion based on project state

**Rules:**
- R1: Show Case 1 format when any SPECs exist in the project
- R2: Show Case 2 format when no SPECs exist
- R3: "최근 완료" line is omitted when no completed SPECs exist

