## A2: Workflow Lifecycle Format

Display after each subcommand (plan, go, sync) completes to show position in the full cycle.

```
🐙 Workflow: {SPEC-ID}
  ✓ plan  →  ● go  →  ○ sync
```

**Status symbols:**
- `✓` — Stage completed
- `●` — Current stage (just completed)
- `○` — Stage pending

**Stage combinations:**

After `plan` completes:
```
🐙 Workflow: {SPEC-ID}
  ● plan  →  ○ go  →  ○ sync
```

After `go` completes:
```
🐙 Workflow: {SPEC-ID}
  ✓ plan  →  ● go  →  ○ sync
```

After `sync` completes:
```
🐙 Workflow: {SPEC-ID}
  ✓ plan  →  ✓ go  →  ● sync
```

